","meaning":"of the absolute certainty (describes عَيْنَ/eye)","transliteration":"l-yaqīni","root":"يقن","lemmaId":null},{"id":"102:8:1","ayahNum":8,"wordNum":1,"word":"ثُمَّ","meaning":"then (connects to لَتُسْـَٔلُنَّ - you will surely be asked)","transliteration":"thumma","root":"","lemmaId":1171},{"id":"102:8:2","ayahNum":8,"wordNum":2,"word":"لَتُسْـَٔلُنَّ","meaning":"you will definitely be asked (about النَّعِيمِ/the blessings)","transliteration":"latus'alunna","root":"سأل","lemmaId":1964},{"id":"102:8:3","ayahNum":8,"wordNum":3,"word":"يَوْمَئِذٍ","meaning":"on that day (when you will be asked about pleasure)","transliteration":"yawma-idhin","root":"يوم","lemmaId":null},{"id":"102:8:4","ayahNum":8,"wordNum":4,"word":"عَنِ","meaning":"about/concerning (connects to لَتُسْـَٔلُنَّ - you will be asked)","transliteration":"ʿani","root":"","lemmaId":4713},{"id":"102:8:5","ayahNum":8,"wordNum":5,"word":"ٱلنَّعِيمِ","meaning":"the comfort/blessing (object of عَنِ)","transliteration":"l-naʿīmi","root":"نعم","lemmaId":4032}]